gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nets 124, Wizards 97
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nets defeated the Wizards, 124-97. Mikal Bridges recorded a game-high 21 points, along with four rebounds and three assists for the Nets, while Cam Thomas added 17 points and four assists in the win. Kyle Kuzma tallied 17 points, three rebounds, and two assists for the Wizards in the defeat. The Nets improve to 12-9 in the regular season, while the Wizards fall to 3-18.
